OL,7,FA lorry driver quit his job within
OL,8,Fminutes of finding out he and his wife
OL,9,Fhad won #166,666 each on the People's
OL,10,FPostcode Lottery, with the couple
OL,11,Fsaying "it feels like a dream".
OL,13,FTony Hedley, 68, pulled his truck onto
OL,14,Fa hard shoulder to take a video call
OL,15,Ffrom his wife Christine, 65, on
OL,16,FThursday, who revealed they had won a
OL,17,Fcombined sum of more than #333,000
OL,18,Fafter purchasing a ticket each in the
OL,19,Fdraw.
