OL,7,FMr Hedley, a grandfather-of-four,
OL,8,Fwasted no time in phoning his employer
OL,9,Ffrom his lorry cab to tell him he
OL,10,Fwouldn't be coming in the following
OL,11,Fday or returning at all, taking
OL,12,Fretirement and a much-needed rest
OL,13,Fafter driving heavy goods lorries for
OL,14,F42 years.
OL,16,FThe couple from Newcastle upon Tyne
OL,17,Fare hoping to use the money to revamp
OL,18,Ftheir bathroom and garden, as well as
OL,19,Fgoing on a family getaway to
OL,20,FPitlochry, Scotland, in August.
