OL,7,F"It was just surreal, it was like the
OL,8,Fweight had lifted off my shoulders,"
OL,9,FMr Hedley told the PA news agency.
OL,11,F"When I finished the call with the
OL,12,FPostcode Lottery, I phoned up work and
OL,13,Fsaid 'when I come back, I'm not coming
OL,14,Fin tomorrow and this is my last shift'.
OL,16,F"I got back to the base, I dropped the
OL,17,Ftrailer off and my manager said, 'you
OL,18,Flucky sod', shook my hand and wished
OL,19,Fme all the best."
