OL,7,FMr Hedley added: "I've been working
OL,8,Fall my life and I think it's time I
OL,9,Fhad a break.
OL,11,F"When they revealed the envelope, it
OL,12,Fwas just surreal."
OL,14,FWhile Mr Hedley was working at the
OL,15,Ftime their win was revealed, Mrs
OL,16,FHedley was at home to open the
OL,17,Fenvelope herself.
OL,19,F"When I pulled the ticket out, I
OL,20,Fcouldn't believe it, I just cried,"
OL,21,Fthe teaching assistant told PA.
