OL,7,F"I never thought it would be that big.
OL,9,F"It's still unbelievable, I wake up in
OL,10,Fthe morning and think 'did I dream
OL,11,Fthat?'"
OL,13,FAs well as making some home
OL,14,Fimprovements, the couple want to use
OL,15,Fthe money to help out their two
OL,16,Fchildren and four grandchildren, along
OL,17,Fwith a great-grandchild on the way.
OL,19,F"We're not the type to go out on
OL,20,Fspending sprees and we don't ask for
OL,21,Fmuch out of life," Mrs Hedley said.
