OL,7,F"I think the first thing is to make
OL,8,Fsure the kids are alright and get
OL,9,Fsomebody in to do the gardens and
OL,10,Fbathroom and renovate the house a bit.
OL,12,F"And then we'll think about it after
OL,13,Fthat and just take things slowly.
OL,15,F"It's lovely to know that we can just
OL,16,Frelax and live life for us now."
OL,18,F"These kinds of things don't happen to
OL,19,Fpeople like us," Mr Hedley said, with
OL,20,Fhis wife adding: "Well, they do now."
